title: Ep.10: Seahawks Get Shutout, Odell's First Game, Steelers/Lions Tie, Super Bowl Predictions, and More...
description: In this episode Griffin and Joe talk about Green Bay's impressive defensive performance, Odell's long awaited debut, the Steelers tying with the worst team in the league, and other random topics coming to mind.
